{"tid":1588601,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新華社批侮辱國旗褻瀆全體中國人民","createTime":"2019-09-23T01:43:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T03:14:38.000Z","uid":56881,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"427038a6fc0305c0140866520ca89f0e6d55f767","tid":1588601,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T01:43:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%96%B0%E8%8F%AF%E7%A4%BE%E6%89%B9%E4%BE%AE%E8%BE%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%97%97%E8%A4%BB%E7%80%86%E5%85%A8%E9%AB%94%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91-235333272.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%2589%25B9%25E4%25BE%25AE%25E8%25BE%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2597%2597%25E8%25A4%25BB%25E7%2580%2586%25E5%2585%25A8%25E9%25AB%2594%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B0%2591-235333272.html&d=ly7kxqs2i5dkBMcnx8uly0zlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=74d8d6f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%96%B0%E8%8F%AF%E7%A4%BE%E6%89%B9%E4%BE%AE%E8%BE%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%97%97%E8%A4%BB%E7%80%86%E5%85%A8%E9%AB%94%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91-235333272.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/uODsoq7teoBvKyRR00_2gQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzU5O2g9MjAyO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/News/now.com/CN-FLAG-190923-07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FuODsoq7teoBvKyRR00_2gQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzU5O2g9MjAyO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2FNews%2Fnow.com%2FCN-FLAG-190923-07.jpg&h=a6d5de56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新華社批侮辱國旗褻瀆全體中國人民<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】內地傳媒批評，有人多次侮辱國旗，是對全體中國人民的褻瀆，呼籲在大是大非面前要作出正確選擇，旗幟鮮明地守護國旗。<br />\n<br />\n新華社發表評論文章，指周日在沙田大會堂有國旗被扯下並遭多人踐踏，亦有人用黑色噴漆塗污國旗，更將國旗扔進垃圾桶裡和附近的城門河中，批評這些行為是喪失良知，背德違法的惡行，凸顯暴徒對國旗與國家的仇恨。<br />\n<br />\n又指3個多月來的修例風波中，侮辱國旗的惡行不斷上演，有國旗被焚燒和扔進大海，做法是對國家和民族的侮辱，更是對全體中國人民的褻瀆。侮辱國旗者除了激起全體中國人民的強烈憤慨，亦違反《國旗法》，必將受到法律嚴懲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又嬲"},{"pid":"211026ace8780fd2e6b6b733f752fc82564c7b68","tid":1588601,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T01:43:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"3a5d0653bf288696ab682c19f7093cc59769c0f4","tid":1588601,"uid":245033,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T01:44:09.000Z","msg":"求警犬踢國旗果張gif<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28ef457a13f78d903ec0b9acc56a7a71ed90f7de","tid":1588601,"uid":25108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T01:44:41.000Z","msg":"又唔係咩大罪<br />\n被拉都抵"},{"pid":"8d70d40c37ec04e02ee360dc99f7d2ca97c0e2fa","tid":1588601,"uid":52459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T01:45:02.000Z","msg":"官方認證，各位手足做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf4d021eed38008181fb149d6628a6bee96f814a","tid":1588601,"uid":60977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T01:45:25.000Z","msg":"黨國不分既下場"},{"pid":"e868897b080dcba643af153dccb977182ab91675","tid":1588601,"uid":44358,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"3a5d0653bf288696ab682c19f7093cc59769c0f4","tid":1588601,"uid":245033,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T01:44:09.000Z","msg":"求警犬踢國旗果張gif<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T01:45:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8Y3D2RA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://